29. Nf3 - after taking control of the c file, manoeuvering my pawns to prevent a knight incursion and backing up my isolated d pawn I decided to offer my opponent a draw.  If I got a refusal I would have centralised Henry but he accepted.  So I achieve another high draw - this time I failed by just 3 rating points to net my first ever rated Expert Draw.  Hope you have had a good read.  Cheers and bye for now.  Joanne
